sqlReaderQuery.value:
select FORMAT(DATEADD(day,16,t1.DateMonthStart),'yyMMdd') as cddte
		from dbo.dim_Date t1
		where CalendarDate = cast (getdate() as date)
		and (DayOfMonth between 1 and 17)
		UNION 
select  FORMAT(DATEADD(day,17,t1.DateMonthEnd),'yyMMdd') as cddte
		from dbo.dim_Date t1
		where CalendarDate = cast (getdate() as date)
		and (DayOfMonth between 18 and 31 )

select JOB_NAME,START_TIME,FINISH_TIME,STATUS, 'PF_PROJECTION' as FBI_JOB_NAME 
from dw.job_monitoring_vw 
where job_name like '%PF_SNAPSHOT_ETL%' 
and status = 'SUCCESS' 
and to_date(finish_time,'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS') > trunc(sysdate)
